Get Going and Search Some Documents!

First, get the software.

1. Install Ruby: http://ruby-lang.org/
2. Install Python: https://www.python.org/
3. Install PostgreSQL: http://www.postgresql.org/
4. Install DocSplit: http://documentcloud.github.io/docsplit/

Second, build the software.

1. Go to the project's directory
2. run `bundle install`
3. run `ruby lib/server.rb`
4. in the "docs" folder, run `python -m SimpleHTTPServer`

Third, use the software.

1. Go to http://localhost:4567/search
2. Search for things "paid overtime"